fields.name: admin_profile_auth
docs: Admin authority for profile related actions (i.e. claim/unclaim profile, vest tokens)

fields.name: admin_migration_auth
docs: Admin authority for liquidity migration related actions (i.e. execute migration, lock liquidity)

fields.name: admin_fee_auth
docs: Admin authority for fee related actions (i.e. collect fees, transfer protocol fees)

fields.name: pregrad_fee_ppm
docs: Fee on pre-graduation fund deposits in PPM

fields.name: pregrad_min_fund_amount
docs: Min fund amount for pre-graduation in lamports

fields.name: pregrad_min_hours
docs: Min hours that can be set for pre-graduation duration

fields.name: pregrad_max_hours
docs: Max hours that can be set for pre-graduation duration

fields.name: pregrad_min_threshold_amount
docs: Min threshold amount that can be set for pre-graduation (in lamports)
(i.e. total fund/deposit amount >= threshold amount to graduate)

fields.name: pregrad_max_threshold_amount
docs: Maximum threshold amount that can be set for pre-graduation (in lamports)

fields.name: pregrad_profile_token_supply
docs: Token supply reserved for the profile owner

fields.name: pregrad_liquidity_token_supply
docs: Token supply reserved for the liquidity pool (i.e. Raydium)

fields.name: pregrad_token_supply
docs: Token supply that will be distributed to the pre-graduation depositors

fields.name: fee_protocol_proportion_ppm
docs: Proportion of the trading fees that should go to the protocol in PPM

fields.name: raydium_fee_config
docs: Raydium fee config that can be used for the liquidity pool

fields.name: raydium_fee_amount
docs: Fee amount to temporarily move to profile_lp to pay for the Raydium pool creation fee
Typically, this amount is the pool fee creation fee + 0.1 SOL

fields.name: enable_migration
docs: Whether liquidity migration actions are enabled

fields.name: enable_profile_owner
docs: Whether profile owner actions are enabled

fields.name: enable_fee
docs: Whether fee related actions are enabled

fields.name: token_uri
docs: URI used in the token metadata

fields.name: social_type
docs: Social type (i.e. X, TikTok, Instagram, etc.)

fields.name: graduation_amount
docs: Total amount of lamports that needs to be deposited for the pre-grad to graduate

fields.name: initial_fund_amount
docs: Amount of lamports that the payer of InitPregrad is depositing

fields.name: locked_lp_amount
docs: The Locked liquidity amount without claimed lp fee

fields.name: last_lp
docs: Last updated cp pool lp total supply

fields.name: pool_id
docs: The ID of the pool with which this record is connected

fields.name: fee_nft_mint
docs: nft mint to check who has authority to collect fee

fields.name: locked_owner
docs: The owner who has locked liquidity

fields.name: locked_lp_mint
docs: The mint of locked lp token

fields.name: event_time
docs: Time migration event occurred (in epoch seconds)

fields.name: lp_mint
docs: Pool tokens are issued when A or B tokens are deposited.
Pool tokens can be withdrawn back to the original A or B token.

fields.name: observation_key
docs: observation account to store oracle data

fields.name: status
docs: Bitwise representation of the state of the pool

fields.name: protocol_fees_token_0
docs: The amounts of token_0 and token_1 that are owed to the liquidity provider.

fields.name: open_time
docs: The timestamp allowed for swap in the pool.

types.name: PregradAddFundEvent
docs: Emitted when a user adds fund to a pre-graduation

fields.name: total_user_fund_amount
docs: Total fund amount added so far by the user

fields.name: event_time
docs: Time fund event occurred (in epoch seconds)

types.name: PregradCompleteEvent
docs: Emitted when a pre-graduation is completed

fields.name: event_time
docs: Time complete event occurred (in epoch seconds)

types.name: PregradDataV1
docs: Data account that keeps track of the pre-graduation phase

fields.name: token_mint
docs: Token tied to the pre-graduation / profile

fields.name: end_time
docs: End time of the pre-graduation in epoch seconds

fields.name: graduation_threshold_amount
docs: Amount required for the pre-grad to graduate (in lamports)
(i.e. total fund/deposit amount >= threshold amount to graduate)

fields.name: profile_token_supply
docs: Token supply reserved for the profile owner

fields.name: liquidity_token_supply
docs: Token supply reserved for the liquidity pool (i.e. Raydium)

fields.name: pregrad_token_supply
docs: Token supply that will be distributed to the pre-graduation depositors

fields.name: total_users
docs: Total number of users that have funded/deposited into the pre-graduation

fields.name: total_fund_amount
docs: Total amount of funds that have been deposited into the pre-graduation (in lamports)

fields.name: refunded_users
docs: Number of users that have been refunded

fields.name: refunded_fund_amount
docs: Total amount of funds/deposits that have been refunded (in lamports)

fields.name: distributed_users
docs: Number of users that have been distributed tokens

fields.name: distributed_fund_amount
docs: Total amount of funds/deposits that have been distributed (in lamports)

fields.name: distributed_token_amount
docs: Total amount of tokens that have been distributed

fields.name: protocol_fee_amount
docs: Amount of protocol fees that have been collected (in lamports)

types.name: PregradDeleteEvent
docs: Emitted when a pre-graduation is deleted

fields.name: event_time
docs: Time delete event occurred (in epoch seconds)

types.name: PregradDistributeTokensEvent
docs: Emitted when a pre-graduation distributes tokens to a user

fields.name: user_token_amount
docs: Amount of tokens distributed to the user

fields.name: user_fund_amount
docs: Amount of fund user added for the token distribution

fields.name: event_time
docs: Time distribute event occurred (in epoch seconds)

types.name: PregradRefundUserEvent
docs: Emitted when a pre-graduation refunds a user

fields.name: user_fund_amount
docs: Amount of fund user added for the token distribution

fields.name: event_time
docs: Time refund event occurred (in epoch seconds)

types.name: PregradUserFundV1
docs: Per-user and per-pregrad account to hold the user's fund amount
Should only exist during the pre-graduation phase

fields.name: fund_amount
docs: Amount of funds/deposits that this user has deposited into the pre-graduation (in lamports)

types.name: ProfileDataV1
docs: Data account that keeps track of the profile

fields.name: allocation_amount
docs: Amount of tokens that is reserved/allocated to the profile owner
This value is fixed at initialization and should not change

fields.name: available_amount
docs: Amount of tokens that are available for the profile owner to vest

fields.name: vested_amount
docs: Amount of tokens that have been vested

fields.name: last_vesting_update_time
docs: Last time vesting occurred/updated (in epoch seconds)

fields.name: protocol_lp_token_fee_amount
docs: Amount of tokens collected from Raydium's LP that protocol owns as fees

fields.name: protocol_lp_quote_fee_amount
docs: Amount of lamports collected from Raydium's LP that protocol owns as fees

fields.name: owner_lp_token_fee_amount
docs: Amount of tokens collected from Raydium's LP that profile owner owns as fees

fields.name: owner_lp_quote_fee_amount
docs: Amount of lamports collected from Raydium's LP that profile owner owns as fees

fields.name: last_owner_social_update_time
docs: Last time the profile_owner address was updated (in epoch seconds)
This happens when the profile owner claims or the protocol unclaims the profile

fields.name: protocol_lp_token_fee_amount
docs: Amount of protocol LP token fees

fields.name: protocol_lp_quote_fee_amount
docs: Amount of protocol LP quote fees

fields.name: owner_lp_token_fee_amount
docs: Amount of owner LP token fees

fields.name: owner_lp_quote_fee_amount
docs: Amount of owner LP quote fees

fields.name: event_time
docs: Time fee event occurred (in epoch seconds)

fields.name: event_time
docs: Time the profile_owner address was updated (in epoch seconds)

types.name: ProfileSelfCustodyEvent
docs: Emitted when profile owner signals self-custody

fields.name: token_amount
docs: Amount of tokens that are subject to self-custody

fields.name: event_time
docs: Time self-custody event occurred (in epoch seconds)

types.name: ProfileTokenVestingEvent
docs: Emitted when profile token amounts change

fields.name: allocation_amount
docs: Amount of tokens that is reserved/allocated to the profile owner

fields.name: available_amount
docs: Amount of tokens that are available for the profile owner to vest

fields.name: vested_amount
docs: Amount of tokens that have been vested

types.name: ProfileVestV1
docs: Account that keeps track of the profile owner's vested tokens and token self-custody process

fields.name: signal_amount
docs: Amount of tokens that the profile owner has signaled to be self-custody
This amount can be self-custodied after the self-custody cooldown period

fields.name: last_signal_time
docs: Last time the profile owner signaled to self-custody the tokens (in epoch seconds)
